wrapScienceJ.process

Enum ProcessInputOutput.OutputDataKind

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ProcessInputOutput.OutputDataKind>
      • wrapScienceJ.process.ProcessInputOutput.OutputDataKind
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ProcessInputOutput.OutputDataKind>
    Enclosing class:
    ProcessInputOutput

    public static enum ProcessInputOutput.OutputDataKind
extends java.lang.Enum<ProcessInputOutput.OutputDataKind>
    Enumeration of different possible cases for the output and processing of a PluginFilterGeneric. Only in the case of EqualsInput is the input image assumed to be changed. In all other cases, the process must leave the image unchanged. In case of CreatedFromInputCopy, the input image has to be duplicated to initialize the current image before running the process.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      ImageCollection
      A List of instances that Implement ImageCore.
      ImageOtherThanInput
      Implements ImageCore but is different from the input image.
      OtherUnspecified
      The output can be anything and the ProcessInputOutput.getOutputDataKind() method must be overridden to use and process the output data.
